definitions.definition: Uncomfortable , especially due to one's surroundings.
examples: I felt so misplaced at that party last night.

definitions.definition: Lost ; disoriented , put in the wrong place .
examples: I was looking for the supermarket but then I got misplaced .

main_definition: Uncomfortable , especially due to one's surroundings.
secondary_definitions: Lost ; disoriented , put in the wrong place .
